== 研發 ==
遊戲開發在2010年之《[[刺客教條：兄弟會|刺客教條：兄弟會]]》完成後不久展開<ref name="GITenThings">{{cite web|url=http://www.gameinformer.com/games/assassins_creed_unity/b/xboxone/archive/2014/06/11/ten-things-you-need-to-know-about-assassin-s-creed-unity.aspx|title=Ten Things You Need To Know About Assassin’s Creed Unity|last=Miller|first=Matt|work=Game Informer|publisher=GameStop|date=2014-06-11|accessdate=2014-06-12|archive-date=2017-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170614141507/http://www.gameinformer.com/games/assassins_creed_unity/b/xboxone/archive/2014/06/11/ten-things-you-need-to-know-about-assassin-s-creed-unity.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>，核心開發小組曾因進行《[[刺客教條III|刺客教條III]]》之早期開發而分裂.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gameinformer.com/b/features/archive/2014/08/22/assassin-s-creed-s-tech-master-leads-us-through-the-series-history.aspx?PostPageIndex=2|title=Assassin’s Creed’s Tech Master Leads Us Through The Series’ History|last=Cork|first=Jeff|publisher=GameStop|work=Game Informer|date=2014-08-22|accessdate=2014-08-22|archive-date=2020-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201026184551/https://www.gameinformer.com/b/features/archive/2014/08/22/assassin-s-creed-s-tech-master-leads-us-through-the-series-history.aspx?PostPageIndex=2|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年3月19日，有關下一部代號為「大革命」的遊戲之圖片被公開，透露了一位身處巴黎的新刺客阿諾、顯示了新的「自由奔跑（上）」和「自由奔跑（下）」按鈕、也表示大革命將定於法國大革命時期，將於2014年末在[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]和[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]平台上發行<ref name="KotakuUnity">{{cite web |url=http://kotaku.com/leaked-images-reveal-one-of-this-falls-two-assassins-1547111652 |title=Leaked Images Reveal One Of This Fall's Two Assassin's Creed Games |last=Schreier |first=Jason |publisher=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]] |date=2014-03-19 |accessdate=2014-03-19 |archive-date=2014-03-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140319222143/http://kotaku.com/leaked-images-reveal-one-of-this-falls-two-assassins-1547111652 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。3月21日，[[育碧軟件|育碧軟件]]透過早期遊戲影片確認遊戲的存在；開發已進行了超過三年，也確認發行日幫為2014年最後一季，也會在微軟視窗上發行<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ign.com/articles/2014/03/21/ubisoft-confirms-assassins-creed-unity-release-date-teased |title=Ubisoft Confirms Assassin's Creed: Unity, Release Date Teased |last=Karmali |first=Luke |publisher=[[IGN|IGN]] |date=2014-03-21 |accessdate=2014-03-21 |archive-date=2020-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114170857/https://www.ign.com/articles/2014/03/21/ubisoft-confirms-assassins-creed-unity-release-date-teased |dead-url=no }}</ref>。育碧劇作家Jeff Yohalem透露法國大革命時代和《刺客教條III》之[[美國革命|美國革命]]已於《刺客教條：兄弟會》結局部分之符號中暗示了<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2014-03-25-assassins-creed-unity-was-teased-in-brotherhood-writer-reveals |title=Assassin's Creed: Unity was teased in Brotherhood, writer reveals |last=Phillips |first=Tom |publisher=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] |date=2014-03-25 |accessdate=2014-06-09 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112000656/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2014-03-25-assassins-creed-unity-was-teased-in-brotherhood-writer-reveals |dead-url=no }}</ref>。育碧蒙特利爾擔任遊戲首席開發，位於[[多倫多|多倫多]]、[[烏克蘭|烏克蘭]]、[[新加坡|新加坡]]、[[上海|上海]]、[[阿納西|阿納西]]、[[蒙彼利埃|蒙彼利埃]]、[[布加勒斯特|布加勒斯特]], [[魁北克|魁北克]]和[[成都|成都]]之分部公司也有參與開發<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/05/15/10-ubisoft-studios-developing-assassins-creed-unity |title=10 Ubisoft Studios Developing Assassin's Creed Unity |last=Dyer |first=Mitch |publisher=[[IGN|IGN]] |date=2014-05-15 |accessdate=2014-05-16 |archive-date=2020-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200726111417/https://www.ign.com/articles/2014/05/15/10-ubisoft-studios-developing-assassins-creed-unity |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

遊戲宣傳片段於2014年[[E3电子娱乐展|E3]]中發佈，公開了系列中首次引進之線上四人合作模式<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/06/09/e3-2014-assassins-creed-unity-co-op-revealed |title=E3 2014: Assassin's Creed Unity Co-Op Revealed |last=Jackson |first=Leah B. |publisher=[[IGN|IGN]] |date=2014-06-09 |accessdate=2014-06-09 |archive-date=2014-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140610192943/http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/06/09/e3-2014-assassins-creed-unity-co-op-revealed |dead-url=no }}</ref>。開發團隊利用新一代遊戲主機的數據處理能力改善了[[非玩家角色|非玩家角色]]群眾，容許多達1000名[[人工智能|人工智能]]角色互相互動或針對玩家行動作出個別反應<ref name="GITenThings" />。由於育碧软件與[[英伟达|英伟达]]宣布自2014年6月4日起建立雙方的合作夥伴關係，遊戲的[[个人电脑|个人电脑]]版本會採用[[英伟达|英伟达]]的GameWorks技術，例如{{translink|en|Temporal anti-aliasing|TXAA}}反鋸齒、先進[[DirectX|DX11]][[密鋪|曲面細分]]以及[[PhysX|PhysX]] [[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]] 以及[[XBOX_ONE|XBOX ONE]] 顯示比PC較低，解析度只有900P，[[个人电脑|PC]]版本為1080P <ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.ubisoftgroup.com/en-US/press/detail.aspx?cid=tcm:99-146531-16&ctid=tcm:95-27313-32 |title=UBISOFT® AND NVIDIA TEAM UP ON ASSASSIN'S CREED® UNITY, FAR CRY® 4, THE CREW™ AND TOM CLANCY'S THE DIVISION™ |accessdate=2014-09-04 |archive-date=2014-10-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141018210956/https://www.ubisoftgroup.com/en-US/press/detail.aspx?cid=tcm:99-146531-16&ctid=tcm:95-27313-32 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.ubisoftgroup.com/comsite_common/en-US/images/Ubisoft_Nvidia_FINALtcm99146534.pdf |title=UBISOFT® AND NVIDIA TEAM UP ON ASSASSIN'S CREED® UNITY, FAR CRY® 4, THE CREW™ AND TOM CLANCY'S THE DIVISION™ |accessdate=2014-09-04 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304190143/https://www.ubisoftgroup.com/comsite_common/en-US/images/Ubisoft_Nvidia_FINALtcm99146534.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/nvidia-working-with-ubisoft-on-assassin-s-creed-unity-far-cry-4-pc/1100-6420130/ |title=Nvidia Working With Ubisoft on Assassin's Creed Unity, Far Cry 4 PC |accessdate=2014-09-04 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112034812/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/nvidia-working-with-ubisoft-on-assassin-s-creed-unity-far-cry-4-pc/1100-6420130/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

遊戲的首席設計師本傑明·布里治表示由於反擊指令被廢除而且守衛更加強悍，遊戲難度會較前作為高<ref>{{cite web|url=http://geekparty.com/assassins-creed-unity-will-be-more-challenging-than-previous-games|title=Assassin’s Creed Unity Will Be More Challenging Than Previous Games|last=Odoerfer|first=Mandi|publisher=GeekParty|date=2014-08-16|accessdate=2014-08-17|archive-date=2017-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170706100100/http://geekparty.com/assassins-creed-unity-will-be-more-challenging-than-previous-games/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，同時表示遊戲包含同步刺殺設定，容許與最多三名玩家進行同步的刺殺<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/assassinscreed/status/500587393716465667|title=.@Maceonik_AC Yeah, you can do Double Assassinations. Even better now because you can synchronize them with three other players! #AskACBen|author=Assassin's Creed|publisher=Twitter|date=2014-08-16|accessdate=2014-08-17|archive-date=2019-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190930070414/https://twitter.com/assassinscreed/status/500587393716465667|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

