由于育碧的送游戏行为<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gamersky.com/news/201411/493027.shtml|title=育碧为众多Bug道歉 《刺客信条：大革命》DLC将免费增送 _ 游民星空 GamerSky.com|accessdate=2016-09-26|work=www.gamersky.com|archive-date=2020-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200408100527/https://www.gamersky.com/news/201411/493027.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>，导致育碧被玩家经常调侃买BUG送游戏<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://pc.265g.com/news/1605/12940.html|title=买bug送游戏 《全境封锁》1.2更新大BUG_新闻资讯_265G单机频道|accessdate=2016-09-26|work=pc.265g.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160927082450/http://pc.265g.com/news/1605/12940.html|archive-date=2016-09-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://play.163.com/14/1218/09/ADO69KKA00314K8K.html|title=俄罗斯方块也能玩出来BUG？育碧游戏再引话题_爱玩网|accessdate=2016-09-26|last=网易|work=play.163.com|archive-date=2019-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609091759/http://play.163.com/14/1218/09/ADO69KKA00314K8K.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
